						               													<description>PopCats Fighter is a 1v1 Take-That and Hand-Management card fighting game inspired by 80&amp;rsquo;s retro arcade games!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Select your favorite PopCat Fighter character, with unique Purrks and Super Moves, to be your champion against your opponent. Build colorful Combos by connecting Move Cards from your hand using COLOR/SHAPE to build the strongest Combo you can, while avoiding making it too vulnerable to your opponent's Defensive abilities!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The more Combos you play, the stronger they get! The more Move Cards you add to your Combo, the higher chance you have to gain a valuable resource called Energy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Energy can help you get the most out of the abilities in your Cards, it can help you Counter Blocks, and even Draw Move Cards! Spending your Energy drawing cards is a great way to add some extra Moves for your stronger Combos, otherwise you will have to wait until after your #3 Combo to draw some new Move Cards on your own. That's assuming you survive Round 1!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Danger slowly creeps up as your Health gets closer to zero, but fear not as you can unlock Raging Furry Mode that will give you an instant Bonus that might just give you the edge you needed to survive!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a medium weight game with layers of strategy. Select your PopCat Fighter from our roster that is made up of 8 contenders like Spawrkles, Purrserker, El Tigre, Catana, Ki-10s, Claw-Fang, Apuma, and Clawdette! All characters come with 2 unique Purrks, and 2 unique Super Moves.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1v1: 45-60 Minutes&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game is set to re-launch on Kickstarter September 2021! If you would like to demo the game now, find PopCats Fighter on Tabletop Simulator's workshop!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
